---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Tarot Card Readings | Free and Personal Readings | Tarot Flower"
  description="Explore free tarot card readings, book a personal reading with Vanessa, or discover Tantric Tarot with Melissa."
  image="/images/2023/04/The-Empress-AI-4-1024x1024.jpg"
>
  <main class="tarot-readings-landing">
    <header class="readings-hero container">
      <h1>Tarot Card Readings</h1>
      <p>The magic isn’t in the cards. It’s in the connection.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <section class="tarot-readings-introduction" aria-label="Introduction to tarot card readings">
        <p>Tarot is a language of symbols, intuition, and reflection.</p>
        <p>A reading can offer a new perspective, illuminate patterns, and bring clarity to something you already feel but may not yet have words for.</p>
        <p>Explore a reading in the way that speaks to you.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="tarot-reading-paths">
        <section class="tarot-reading-path">
          <div class="tarot-reading-path-image">
            <img
              src="/images/2023/04/The-Empress-AI-4-1024x1024.jpg"
              alt="The Empress surrounded by flowers in colorful tarot artwork"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="tarot-reading-path-copy">
            <h2>Free Tarot Card Readings</h2>
            <p>Choose the reading that calls to you and receive the message waiting beneath the cards.</p>
            <p>These timeless readings are created for moments when you need reflection, reassurance, or a different way of seeing what is unfolding in your life.</p>
            <a class="readings-button" href="/free-tarot-card-readings/">Explore Free Readings</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="tarot-reading-path tarot-reading-path--reverse">
          <div class="tarot-reading-path-copy tarot-reading-path-booking">
            <h2>Readings with Vanessa</h2>
            <p>A personal, one-on-one tarot reading designed around your questions, your life, and the moment you are navigating.</p>
            <p>Together, we’ll explore the cards, the patterns unfolding around you, and the possibilities available to you now.</p>
            <p class="tarot-reading-format">60-minute online reading</p>
            <p class="tarot-reading-price">$100 USD</p>
            <a class="readings-button" href="/readings-with-vanessa/">Book a Reading</a>
          </div>
          <div class="tarot-reading-path-image tarot-reading-path-image--vanessa">
            <img
              src="/images/readings-with-vanessa/vanessa-holding-empress-card.png"
              alt="Vanessa smiling while holding the Empress tarot card"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="tarot-reading-path">
          <div class="tarot-reading-path-image tarot-reading-path-image--melissa">
            <img
              src="/images/2024/05/Melissa-Warwood-Tantric-Tarot-3.jpeg"
              alt="Melissa Warwood, Tantric Tarot reader"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="tarot-reading-path-copy">
            <h2>Tantric Tarot by Melissa</h2>
            <p>A deeply intuitive approach to tarot that explores the relationship between energy, embodiment, intimacy, and transformation.</p>
            <p>Discover Melissa’s unique work and the perspective she brings to the cards.</p>
            <a class="readings-button" href="/melissa-warwood-tantric-tarot/">Discover Tantric Tarot</a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="tarot-readings-closing">
        <h2>The Reader Is Part of the Reading</h2>
        <p>The cards may open the door, but the connection between the question, the reader, and the moment is where the reading comes alive.</p>
        <p>Choose the doorway that feels right for you.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
